  <p>
    In the following exercises, a list of transformations is given.
    Find the matrix <m>A</m> that performs those transformations,
    in order, on the Cartesian plane.
  </p>
  <exercise>
    <statement>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <p>
            vertical shear by a factor of 2
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
