    </statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        Yes, these are the same.
        Each produces the transformation matrix <m>\left[\begin{array}{cc} 0 \amp 1 \\ -1 \amp 0 \end{array} \right]</m>.
      </p>
    </answer>
